CFS Checksum Commands

CFS Checksum Telemetry CFS Checksum Table Definitions CFS Checksum Configuration Parameters

The following is a list of Commands that are processed by the CFS Checksum Application.

Global CS_CANCEL_ONESHOT_CC
Cancel one shot

Global CS_DISABLE_ALL_CS_CC
Disable Global Checksumming

Global CS_DISABLE_APPS_CC
Disable checksumming for App table

Global CS_DISABLE_CFECORE_CC
Disable checksumming of cFE core

Global CS_DISABLE_EEPROM_CC

Global CS_DISABLE_ENTRY_MEMORY_CC

Global CS_DISABLE_MEMORY_CC
